  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We rented one room in a pension.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We had no cooking facilities, so we had food delivered from a neighborhood restaurant.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember where that was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[HUNGARIAN].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the owner-- the owner of that-- the reason why-- this was actually a very interesting pension, because the-- the owner was a Berliner lady, who had been the secretary of my Hungarian uncle, whom I haven't talked about yet, while he was working in the German war ministry during the First World War as an-- as an Austrian [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [GERMAN], as an officer making contact between the Austrian and German armies.",
      "word_count": 75
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it's not information.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "An officer whose job was to communicate between the two armies.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So anyway, this lady was his secretary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I suspect at one point during the First World War, they must have lovers, because she never failed to mention how good-looking an officer my uncle was during that time.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, she, in the later course became secretary as well as lover with a Jewish physician, by the name of Anheim in Berlin, who-- who I remember quite well, who was a-- was a physician working in working-class areas in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And so I think he saved them by bringing them to Hungary illegally.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he lived illegally in the same apartment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I will never quite forget that he-- you know, he couldn't leave except at night, for fear of being captured.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He grew mice for scientific experiments to keep himself amused, which of course we boys thought was a big thing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He had an enormous library there, obviously an intellectual.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anheim was his name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember that one night he didn't return from going in the street.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
